				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">OK, I've stayed out of Tier #2 to this point, except for some rare group stuff.  I've grouped in Storms, but I've never entered BoT or HoH.
<br />

<br />
I'm 65 with 30ish AAs and moderate/low gear.  Have all my spells, though.
<br />

<br />
I looked a bit around the compendium, but didn't really get my answers.
<br />

<br />
So.  Can I solo tier #2 at all?  Isn't BoT the place where I can fire up the ole Call of the Arch Mage?
<br />

<br />
I'd really like to try charming something and laying the smack down in BoT, but A) anybody got a good strategy?  or B)am I just going to die?
<br />

<br />
Oh. Please do yell at me if this has been covered <span style="font-style: italic">ad nauseum</span>.  Just please leave the link for me?
<br />

<br />
Thanks!</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
