			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">When I'm bored, I solo BoT. There are a hundred guides, but here's mine.
<br />

<br />
Bind at the zone in to BoT in Tranquility.
<br />

<br />
Spell lineup: Elemental Silence, Malosinia, CotAM, Burnout V, Sun Vortex, Gate, Veil of Elements.
<br />

<br />
Cast Veil, and scout for elementals. I prefer the Kjals in the south wing, as there are lots of spots in south that are easy to get them from. When you have a likely elemental selected, stand as far back as possible without aggro-ing other mobs.
<br />

<br />
1. Cast elemental silence. If resisted, you can probably get off another cast before you die.
<br />
2. Once mezzed, malosinia the elemental. Once a mob has been malosinia'd, charm will stick much longer, and mez will always land.
<br />
3. CotAM the mob, and Burnout V it. Your pet is now hell on wheels.
<br />
4. Select a victim, send the pet in, get as far away as possible, and nuke once. Caster mobs go down especially fast... jord profets are my favorite target.
<br />
5. When the mob dies, if there is another one very close, you can send the pet after it too. I do not usually do this, I usually go straight to...
<br />
6. Gate. Cast Veil of Elements, zone in, loot your victim, and repeat.
<br />

<br />
The repeat cycle is a lot easier, as your former pet is waiting for you, still Malosinia'd and Burned Out, and much easier to charm. On a second use, I skip steps 1 and 2, preferring to CotAM and attack my next target. After a couple/few uses, I will re-mez/re-malosinia.
<br />

<br />
I get 3-4aa exp per kill, kills are quick, and the loot is nice. It's not much better than group exp, and the likelihood of death runs around 30% on the initial try, so be prepared to drag your corpse to the nearest noodle cleric.<br />_________________<br />Home-brewin' Youth Pastor
<br />
65 Gnomish Summonin' Foolio
<br />
<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=679031" target="_blank" class="postlink">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=679031</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
	</tr>
