				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">As a side note/report, I've probably completed at least an AA this way, counting lost exp for rezzes. Now that I've been doing it awhile, I very rarely die... because I gate after each dead mob (with RARE exceptions for when there are two immediately next to each other).
<br />

<br />
Overall, it's definitely the fastest loot/exp for a solo mage, and it can be done naked while waiting for whatever raid you died on. Very handy.<br />_________________<br />Home-brewin' Youth Pastor
