The game is going to change very drastically for you.  I'm sorry to be the messenger, but right now you're in the sweet spot for mage power.  When you hit the 50's, you'll find soloing effficiency decreases dramatically and you'll have to group to get decent exp - of course your DPS is subpar at those levels due to your lack of innate mana regen, so become a crack addict to hide your deficiencies.  And hopefully, your group mates will think that since 61+ Mages are good sustained DPS, they'll give a 50-something Mage an invite.  <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="Smile" border="0" /></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
